                                                             &none &mkp LCLK &mkp RCLK &none
                                                    //5way  CLICK       RIGHT       DOWN      LEFT      UP 
                                                            &mkp MCLK   &kp RIGHT   &kp DOWN  &kp LEFT  &kp UP
