                &sk LGUI      &sk LALT       &sk LCTRL       &sk LSHFT       &kp C_VOL_DN   &kp C_MUTE     &kp LEFT       &kp DOWN       &kp UP         &kp RIGHT
                               &kp HOME       &kp PG_DN      &kp END                                       &kp HOME       &kp PG_UP      &kp END
